Package: kungconnect-agent
Version: VERSION_PLACEHOLDER
Architecture: ARCH_PLACEHOLDER
Maintainer: KungConnect <support@kungconnect.app>
Depends: debconf, systemd
Description: KungConnect remote-management agent
 Connects this machine to a KungConnect server and enables secure
 remote desktop management via an encrypted WebRTC session.
 The agent runs as a systemd service and starts automatically at boot.
